# Task 01 – Hello World Program

## Aim

To write a simple Python program that displays the message "Hello World" on the screen.

## Problem Statement

Create a Python program that prints the text "Hello World" when executed.

## Algorithm

1. Start the program.
2. Display the message "Hello World".
3. End the program.

## Flowchart

Start
↓
Display "Hello World"
↓
Stop

## Python Program

print("Hello World")

## Output

Hello World

## Result

The program was executed successfully and displayed the message "Hello World" on the screen.
